692
00:40:22.662 --> 00:40:25.070
- Oh, what? Are you okay?
- I think so.

693
00:40:25.090 --> 00:40:26.481
I mean, luckily I wasn't alone.

694
00:40:26.499 --> 00:40:28.073
Oh. Oh?

695
00:40:28.093 --> 00:40:30.334
- Grant was here.
- Oh, okay.

696
00:40:30.487 --> 00:40:32.095
Well, where is he now?

697
00:40:32.322 --> 00:40:33.504
He's gone ahead to the
restaurant.

698
00:40:33.657 --> 00:40:35.673
I mean, the poor guy stayed up
with me all night.

699
00:40:35.767 --> 00:40:38.768
Oh, that's good.
Did they take anything, or...?

700
00:40:38.920 --> 00:40:41.345
That's the strange part.
They didn't take anything.

701
00:40:41.498 --> 00:40:43.422
I don't know. You know what?

702
00:40:43.442 --> 00:40:46.109
- You wanna just come inside?
- Okay. Yeah, of course.

703
00:40:51.341 --> 00:40:53.432
