like this?

704
00:40:53.452 --> 00:40:55.176
I don't know,
but the crazy part is,

705
00:40:55.269 --> 00:40:57.287
They were still here
when I got home.

706
00:40:57.438 --> 00:40:59.772
I mean, things could have gone
much worse, tess.

707
00:40:59.866 --> 00:41:02.608
And they didn't take anything,
so this wasn't a robbery?

708
00:41:02.627 --> 00:41:04.294
No, I guess not.

709
00:41:04.521 --> 00:41:06.370
I mean, this was the only thing
that was damaged.

710
00:41:06.523 --> 00:41:08.539
- It's broken.
- Oh.

711
00:41:08.692 --> 00:41:10.541
So...

712
00:41:10.635 --> 00:41:12.877
This was personal.

713
00:41:12.971 --> 00:41:15.196
You don't think roger could
have done it?

714
00:41:15.215 --> 00:41:16.789
I mean, who else would have
a reason?

715
00:41:16.883 --> 00:41:18.866
I know. I mean...

716
00:41:18.885 --> 00:41:20.793
Look, roger's done some
awful things,

717
00:41:20.812 --> 00:41:23.204
But I can't imagine him
being capable

718
00:41:23.223 --> 00:41:24.647
Of doing something like this,
you know?

719
00:41:25.892 --> 00:41:27.875
- What next?
- Well, the police said

720
00:41:27.969 --> 00:41:29.486
