either way,

721
00:41:29.713 --> 00:41:31.879
So we'll see what comes of it.
But...

722
00:41:31.973 --> 00:41:33.823
I don't know. I don't know.

723
00:41:33.975 --> 00:41:36.826
Whatever happens, you're not
staying here alone tonight.

724
00:41:37.053 --> 00:41:39.721
Why don't you come stay with me
for a few days?

725
00:41:39.814 --> 00:41:41.331
I really don't want
to stay alone,

726
00:41:41.558 --> 00:41:43.166
But I also don't want to impose
on you like that.

727
00:41:43.317 --> 00:41:44.742
I know how much you like
your space.

728
00:41:44.836 --> 00:41:46.561
Oh, okay, alright.

729
00:41:46.654 --> 00:41:48.588
I will make my chicken parm
sliders.

730
00:41:50.400 --> 00:41:52.491
Thanks, tess. I owe you.

