732
00:41:54.571 --> 00:41:56.012
What is it?

733
00:41:57.665 --> 00:41:58.831
Oh, great.

734
00:41:58.925 --> 00:42:01.518
Something is up at
the restaurant. It's grant.

735
00:42:01.669 --> 00:42:03.353
I gotta go. Come on.

736
00:42:08.860 --> 00:42:10.676
Grant?
Everything alright?

737
00:42:10.695 --> 00:42:12.862
I just got off the phone with
the police.

738
00:42:13.089 --> 00:42:15.114
- Jacqueline is on her way.
