754
00:43:01.562 --> 00:43:02.728
Oh, I'm sorry.

755
00:43:02.747 --> 00:43:04.972
But I didn't see anything else.
Just, um...

756
00:43:04.991 --> 00:43:07.399
I mean, nothing like this.

757
00:43:07.493 --> 00:43:10.086
You know what? They didn't even
check the cash register.

758
00:43:11.664 --> 00:43:13.089
I think this was personal.

759
00:43:15.985 --> 00:43:17.501
Roger.

760
00:43:17.654 --> 00:43:19.821
- It has to be.
- Wait...

761
00:43:19.839 --> 00:43:21.672
You think your ex would do
something like this?

762
00:43:21.766 --> 00:43:24.342
- You think he's this petty?
