763
00:43:24.436 --> 00:43:26.494
I mean, it's something I'm gonna
have to ask him myself.

764
00:43:26.512 --> 00:43:28.271
This is... This is insane.

765
00:43:31.517 --> 00:43:33.776
It's okay, you don't have to do
that, I'll take care of this.

766
00:43:34.003 --> 00:43:35.260
- It's fine.
- Jacqueline: I'm here!

767
00:43:35.355 --> 00:43:36.446
Show me the damage.

768
00:43:38.675 --> 00:43:40.842
Oh my god, it's true.

769
00:43:40.935 --> 00:43:42.619
- Was anybody hurt?
- No.

770
00:43:44.514 --> 00:43:45.863
- What did they take?
- Well, apparently

771
00:43:45.957 --> 00:43:48.941
They took grant's tools, but the
cash register wasn't touched

772
00:43:48.960 --> 00:43:52.536
And nothing else was stolen.
Just...

773
00:43:52.689 --> 00:43:54.797
Oh, this beautiful work.

774
00:43:55.024 --> 00:43:56.782
Ruined.

775
00:43:56.801 --> 00:44:00.044
Oh, that is such a violation.

776
00:44:00.138 --> 00:44:03.364
I think I can still make this
work if I could just

777
00:44:03.457 --> 00:44:06.476
Have a little more time,
I can fix this.

778
00:44:06.627 --> 00:44:08.645
You really think you can
fix this?

779
00:44:08.796 --> 00:44:11.130
Yes, if you could just
give me...

780
00:44:11.149 --> 00:44:14.542
- Just another two weeks or so.
- Another two weeks?

781
00:44:14.560 --> 00:44:16.819
- I needed this ready by Friday.
- I know.

