Now what we're going to do

1036
00:58:11.322 --> 00:58:13.638
Is make a little video

1037
00:58:13.657 --> 00:58:16.492
Where you are going to say that,

1038
00:58:16.643 --> 00:58:20.387
And you're going to tell the
whole world the truth

1039
00:58:20.405 --> 00:58:23.499
About the real ashley morris,
your best friend.

1040
00:58:33.085 --> 00:58:34.918
- (door creaking open)
- ashley: Tess?

1041
00:58:35.012 --> 00:58:36.327
You home?

1042
00:58:36.347 --> 00:58:37.495
(water running)

1043
00:58:37.515 --> 00:58:38.680
Tess?

1044
00:58:40.017 --> 00:58:41.683
(water running)

1045
00:58:53.088 --> 00:58:54.196
Ow.

1046
00:59:12.699 --> 00:59:14.365
Tess, I'm standing in
your kitchen

1047
00:59:14.459 --> 00:59:15.792
Wondering where the hell
you are.

1048
00:59:15.944 --> 00:59:17.386
Call me back, please.

1049
00:59:21.617 --> 00:59:22.558
(sighing)

1050
00:59:30.216 --> 00:59:32.976
(cell phone ringing)

1051
00:59:33.128 --> 00:59:34.978
Finally, I've been calling you
all morning.

1052
00:59:35.072 --> 00:59:36.646
Where are you?

1053
00:59:36.740 --> 00:59:37.906
Marco:
Ashley.

1054
00:59:45.140 --> 00:59:47.732
- Where is tess?
- (marco chuckling)

1055
00:59:47.826 --> 00:59:49.418
You think you could attack me
and I wouldn't defend myself?

1056
00:59:53.424 --> 00:59:55.498
What is this, revenge?

1057
00:59:55.651 --> 00:59:57.426
Is that why you're here?

1058
00:59:57.653 --> 00:59:59.177
This has nothing to do with
revenge.

1059
01:00:00.246 --> 01:00:01.988
Then what do you want, marco?

1060
01:00:02.082 --> 01:00:04.324
I want my reputation back!

1061
01:00:04.343 --> 01:00:07.102
I want you to publicly retract
all the lies you told about me.

1062
01:00:07.329 --> 01:00:09.420
I want everyone
to hear you confess.

1063
01:00:09.440 --> 01:00:12.090
Reputation? How?

1064
01:00:12.109 --> 01:00:14.592
I can't, it's long gone.
I mean,

1065
01:00:14.612 --> 01:00:17.279
You can't put an explosion back
in the bomb, marco.

1066
01:00:18.782 --> 01:00:20.449
So there's no way to
convince you?

1067
01:00:24.029 --> 01:00:27.789
(muffled yelping)

1068
01:00:29.609 --> 01:00:31.710
- How about now?
- (phone chiming)

1069
01:00:35.799 --> 01:00:37.115
Oh my god, tess!

1070
01:00:37.209 --> 01:00:38.783
No, no, no, no! Please!

1071
01:00:38.802 --> 01:00:41.136
What are you doing?
Let her go, marco!

1072
01:00:41.287 --> 01:00:44.197
She goes free the moment that
you admit publicly

1073
01:00:44.216 --> 01:00:46.032
That you lied about me.

1074
01:00:46.051 --> 01:00:47.458
(whimpering)

1075
01:00:47.478 --> 01:00:50.294
I can't! How would I do that?
I mean, it's not just me!

1076
01:00:50.314 --> 01:00:53.039
What do you want me to do, like,
I'm not the only one

1077
01:00:53.058 --> 01:00:54.966
Telling my story. There are
hundreds of us out there.

1078
01:00:55.060 --> 01:00:56.393
Do you realize that?

1079
01:00:56.545 --> 01:00:59.637
Please let her go, please.
She's done nothing to you.

1080
01:00:59.657 --> 01:01:01.564
Marco: She helped destroy
my reputation!

1081
01:01:01.659 --> 01:01:04.326
She's done nothing?
She couldn't do anymore!

1082
01:01:06.664 --> 01:01:08.479
Ashley: I don't know what you
want from me, seriously.

1083
01:01:08.573 --> 01:01:10.907
I don't...
(whimpering)

1084
01:01:11.001 --> 01:01:13.651
Look, um,

1085
01:01:13.671 --> 01:01:15.170
I'll do what you want, okay?
I'll...

1086
01:01:15.397 --> 01:01:17.898
Just please don't hurt her,
okay?

1087
01:01:17.916 --> 01:01:20.583
Um, you want-- you want public
attention, that's what you want?

1088
01:01:20.678 --> 01:01:22.085
I'll do it, okay?

1089
01:01:22.237 --> 01:01:25.329
Um, maybe we can...

1090
01:01:25.424 --> 01:01:29.518
We can go somewhere together in
public for everyone to see.

1091
01:01:31.079 --> 01:01:32.187
What are you talking about?

1092
01:01:32.338 --> 01:01:35.691
Look, um,
the restaurant, okay?

1093
01:01:35.842 --> 01:01:38.601
They're having a grand opening
tomorrow night.

1094
01:01:38.754 --> 01:01:41.179
Okay, and we can go there
together,

1095
01:01:41.273 --> 01:01:43.532
Like a real date, okay?

1096
01:01:43.683 --> 01:01:45.183
And everyone will see
us together

1097
01:01:45.202 --> 01:01:46.927
And see what a gentleman
you are,

1098
01:01:46.945 --> 01:01:48.945
And that's what you want, right?
That's what...?

1099
01:01:49.039 --> 01:01:50.038
That's what...

1100
01:01:54.211 --> 01:01:55.693
No, you're trying to trick me.

1101
01:01:55.787 --> 01:01:58.788
You think that
I'm just some...

1102
01:01:58.882 --> 01:02:01.958
...Stupid little boy asking you
out for pie.

1103
01:02:02.110 --> 01:02:03.944
No, I'm not a fool, ashley.

1104
01:02:03.962 --> 01:02:04.961
(whimpering)

1105
01:02:05.055 --> 01:02:07.705
I swear, I will do it.
Please, I will.

1106
01:02:07.799 --> 01:02:10.726
I'm not lying, just promise me
you'll let her go, please.

1107
01:02:15.733 --> 01:02:17.065
Marco?

1108
01:02:21.296 --> 01:02:22.571
Marco?

1109
01:02:24.074 --> 01:02:25.407
Are you there?

1110
01:02:28.637 --> 01:02:29.986
Okay, okay.

1111
01:02:30.080 --> 01:02:32.063
We'll do it your way.

1112
01:02:32.082 --> 01:02:34.641
But if I see even one cop there,
just one,

1113
01:02:34.659 --> 01:02:36.585
You will never see your friend
again.

1114
01:02:39.757 --> 01:02:42.591
So, how's tomorrow night at
eight o'clock?

1115
01:02:42.742 --> 01:02:44.843
Yeah, yeah, tomorrow night.
Eight o'clock, yeah.

1116
01:02:50.934 --> 01:02:53.602
(sobbing)

1117
01:02:55.773 --> 01:02:57.689
- Grant?
- Hey.

1118
01:02:59.109 --> 01:03:01.851
Are you okay?

1119
01:03:02.004 --> 01:03:03.670
- No.
- Come here.

1120
01:03:03.763 --> 01:03:05.688
No, I don't know what to do.

1121
01:03:05.841 --> 01:03:07.265
I don't know what to do.

1122
01:03:07.284 --> 01:03:08.784
- (crying)
- it's all right.

1123
01:03:08.935 --> 01:03:10.452
It's okay. It's okay.

1124
01:03:10.679 --> 01:03:13.013
Talk to me.

1125
01:03:13.031 --> 01:03:14.790
I know who's behind all
the break-ins.

1126
01:03:15.017 --> 01:03:16.699
He's been stalking me,
the guy I told you, marco,

1127
01:03:16.794 --> 01:03:17.700
The one I met online.

1128
01:03:17.795 --> 01:03:19.352
- It's him!
- Right.

1129
01:03:19.371 --> 01:03:22.188
And he's the one who attacked
roger, and now he has tess!

1130
01:03:22.207 --> 01:03:23.857
(stammers) w-what do you mean he
has tess?

1131
01:03:23.950 --> 01:03:25.783
He just-- he took her!
He just took her.

1132
01:03:25.803 --> 01:03:27.118
He took her somewhere,
I don't know--

1133
01:03:27.137 --> 01:03:29.120
- I don't know where.
- Did you call the police?

1134
01:03:29.139 --> 01:03:31.714
No, I can't, I mean, he said
he'd hurt her if I do.

1135
01:03:31.867 --> 01:03:33.383
I don't know what to do.

1136
01:03:33.477 --> 01:03:37.220
He told me if I do anything,
he'll hurt her,

1137
01:03:37.372 --> 01:03:39.147
So I don't know if I should
call the cops,

1138
01:03:39.299 --> 01:03:40.557
I don't know if that's...
(sniffing)

1139
01:03:40.709 --> 01:03:42.892
This is all my fault.
I shouldn't have done this.

1140
01:03:43.045 --> 01:03:44.319
I shouldn't have gone after him
like that,

1141
01:03:44.546 --> 01:03:46.822
As if revenge was going to make
me feel better.

1142
01:03:47.049 --> 01:03:48.715
No, no, no,
it wasn't about revenge.

1143
01:03:48.808 --> 01:03:50.308
It was about justice, right?

1144
01:03:50.327 --> 01:03:53.053
We can't let people
do this to us,

1145
01:03:53.071 --> 01:03:56.665
Use our trust against us
like that, right?

1146
01:03:56.892 --> 01:03:58.725
Yeah, but...

1147
01:03:58.743 --> 01:04:00.894
I mean, what have I done?

1148
01:04:00.987 --> 01:04:02.245
I don't know what to do now.

1149
01:04:02.339 --> 01:04:04.747
Like, it's just...

1150
01:04:04.842 --> 01:04:07.917
It's like, one thing after
another, you know?

1151
01:04:08.070 --> 01:04:10.828
It all started the night
we went out for pie,

1152
01:04:10.922 --> 01:04:13.098
And it's... It's, um...

1153
01:04:15.410 --> 01:04:17.102
- That's the night--
- what?

1154
01:04:21.007 --> 01:04:22.765
The night we went out
for our pie.

1155
01:04:22.918 --> 01:04:23.859
Mm-hmm.

1156
01:04:27.939 --> 01:04:29.447
- He...
- Ashley?

1157
01:04:31.109 --> 01:04:32.868
(breathing shakily)

1158
01:05:00.397 --> 01:05:03.214
Let's, uh,
let's play some music, yeah?

1159
01:05:03.233 --> 01:05:06.292
- Just to lighten the mood.
- Sure.

1160
01:05:06.386 --> 01:05:09.237
I'm just really depressed.

1161
01:05:09.389 --> 01:05:10.888
(playing rock music)

1162
01:05:10.908 --> 01:05:14.743
♪

1163
01:05:14.970 --> 01:05:15.818
Do you...

1164
01:05:15.913 --> 01:05:18.914
Do you think he's listening
to us?

1165
01:05:19.065 --> 01:05:22.308
I know he's been listening
to us.

1166
01:05:22.327 --> 01:05:23.835
What do you want to do?

1167
01:05:25.422 --> 01:05:27.255
I have a plan.

1168
01:05:29.484 --> 01:05:32.243
But first we need to take out
the trash.

1169
01:05:32.337 --> 01:05:33.762
♪ ...The smoking gun ♪

1170
01:05:37.250 --> 01:05:39.826
♪ this life's
for having fun ♪

1171
01:05:39.844 --> 01:05:44.255
♪

1172
01:05:44.274 --> 01:05:45.941
♪ blood blister ♪

1173
01:05:46.092 --> 01:05:47.167
(clattering)

1174
01:05:47.185 --> 01:05:48.276
♪ blood sister ♪

1175
01:05:56.511 --> 01:05:57.535
Jacqueline:
Ashley?

1176
01:06:00.198 --> 01:06:01.514
(gasping)

1177
01:06:01.607 --> 01:06:04.200
I can't believe
what you've done here.

1178
01:06:04.294 --> 01:06:08.279
The cracks and imperfections
give it such character.

1179
01:06:08.298 --> 01:06:09.447
Yeah.

1180
01:06:09.466 --> 01:06:12.542
Like old dried leather
in the desert sun.

1181
01:06:12.694 --> 01:06:14.452
Was this your plan all along?

1182
01:06:14.471 --> 01:06:17.389
Oh, no. No, this was all
improvised.

1183
01:06:19.643 --> 01:06:22.385
It's like that japanese
pottery art.

1184
01:06:22.537 --> 01:06:24.387
Kisumi, I believe it's called.

1185
01:06:24.481 --> 01:06:25.722
Kintsugi.

1186
01:06:25.874 --> 01:06:26.889
Jacqueline:
That's the one.

1187
01:06:26.984 --> 01:06:28.041
Yeah.

1188
01:06:28.134 --> 01:06:30.318
Oh, I only wish
it wasn't too late.

1189
01:06:30.470 --> 01:06:32.487
I've already cancelled
the reservations.

1190
01:06:32.714 --> 01:06:34.731
The reopening has been
postponed,

1191
01:06:34.883 --> 01:06:37.383
I've resigned myself to
sucking up the loss.

1192
01:06:37.402 --> 01:06:38.660
Well...

1193
01:06:38.811 --> 01:06:41.645
Actually, um,

1194
01:06:41.665 --> 01:06:45.558
Grant and I might have an idea
how you can fill this place,

1195
01:06:45.651 --> 01:06:48.061
If you're willing to open
tomorrow night

1196
01:06:48.079 --> 01:06:51.506
From a private, one-time
seating.

1197
01:06:51.657 --> 01:06:54.175
Look, jacqueline,
I'm not the one who broke into

1198
01:06:54.402 --> 01:06:57.345
Your restaurant and violated
your pride and joy,

1199
01:06:57.572 --> 01:06:59.589
But if you help me,

1200
01:06:59.683 --> 01:07:02.742
If you give me a chance
to set this straight,

1201
01:07:02.761 --> 01:07:06.079
I can deliver you
the son of a bitch who did.

1202
01:07:06.097 --> 01:07:11.985
♪

1203
01:07:14.364 --> 01:07:15.864
I never had any doubt.

1204
01:07:17.108 --> 01:07:18.158
(chuckling)

1205
01:07:21.096 --> 01:07:22.120
(sighing)

1206
01:07:37.128 --> 01:07:38.386
(clearing throat)

1207
01:07:38.538 --> 01:07:40.630
Ashley, ashley,
I am begging you,

1208
01:07:40.782 --> 01:07:41.872
You can't go through with this.

1209
01:07:41.892 --> 01:07:43.874
You don't know what this guy
is capable of.

1210
01:07:43.894 --> 01:07:45.468
Yes, you're still gonna be
in public,

1211
01:07:45.620 --> 01:07:47.303
But you're still gonna be alone.

1212
01:07:47.455 --> 01:07:49.305
Not if you're there with me.

1213
01:07:49.457 --> 01:07:51.624
I... I can't, I won't.

1214
01:07:51.643 --> 01:07:54.644
I just, I can't watch you put
yourself in danger like this.

1215
01:07:54.796 --> 01:07:56.479
You need to call the police.

1216
01:07:56.631 --> 01:07:58.648
Ashley: But then what's going
to happen to tess?

1217
01:07:58.742 --> 01:08:02.151
I mean, how could I live with
myself if she gets hurt?

1218
01:08:02.245 --> 01:08:03.486
I'm sorry, grant.

1219
01:08:03.638 --> 01:08:05.229
I've made up my mind, okay?

1220
01:08:05.323 --> 01:08:06.915
I'm doing this,
with or without you.

1221
01:08:07.976 --> 01:08:09.142
Well, I'm sorry, ashley.

1222
01:08:09.235 --> 01:08:11.252
It's gonna have to be
without me, then.

1223
01:08:12.497 --> 01:08:13.663
I'm done.

1224
01:08:13.815 --> 01:08:15.331
- Goodbye.
- Grant!

1225
01:08:15.483 --> 01:08:16.424
Grant!

1226
01:08:17.743 --> 01:08:20.595
Poor bitter ashley.

1227
01:08:20.746 --> 01:08:22.263
Always being let down.

1228
01:08:24.659 --> 01:08:27.602
Well, I'll show her
what a real man looks like.

1229
01:08:32.517 --> 01:08:33.608
(door slamming)

1230
01:08:41.785 --> 01:08:44.119
Good evening, welcome.

1231
01:08:44.270 --> 01:08:45.537
Your table is waiting.

1232
01:08:47.440 --> 01:08:49.440
Hello, good evening.

1233
01:08:49.459 --> 01:08:50.917
Thank you for coming.

1234
01:08:52.537 --> 01:08:54.420
- Hi.
- Hi.

1235
01:08:57.467 --> 01:08:59.300
Hello, welcome.
Thanks for coming.

1236
01:09:00.528 --> 01:09:01.636
(cell phone chiming)

1237
01:09:04.307 --> 01:09:06.432
Good evening,
we have you right over here.

1238
01:09:07.886 --> 01:09:17.986
♪

1239
01:09:19.656 --> 01:09:21.156
Ashley.

1240
01:09:22.734 --> 01:09:25.476
- Hi.
- In person, finally.

1241
01:09:25.570 --> 01:09:28.121
Wow, you look incredible.

1242
01:09:29.315 --> 01:09:30.415
Thank you.

1243
01:09:41.586 --> 01:09:44.587
Well, I'm here,

1244
01:09:44.681 --> 01:09:46.255
In public,

1245
01:09:46.408 --> 01:09:49.017
With you, for everyone to see.

1246
01:09:49.244 --> 01:09:51.093
So... Where's tess?

1247
01:09:51.246 --> 01:09:52.604
She's okay.

1248
01:09:54.933 --> 01:09:56.840
For now. The rest is up to you.

1249
01:09:56.935 --> 01:09:58.342
If you hurt her--

1250
01:09:58.361 --> 01:10:00.344
Don't be so pessimistic here.

1251
01:10:00.438 --> 01:10:02.346
Just give me your hand.

1252
01:10:02.440 --> 01:10:04.365
- What?
- I said give me your hand.

1253
01:10:11.282 --> 01:10:12.498
Was that so hard?

1254
01:10:13.935 --> 01:10:15.501
You smell like cheap motel soap.

1255
01:10:22.368 --> 01:10:24.052
You're hurting me.

1256
01:10:34.639 --> 01:10:35.730
I'm just...

1257
01:10:39.903 --> 01:10:41.569
I was just trying to calm you.

1258
01:10:45.316 --> 01:10:46.649
Hey, fine. Whatever.

1259
01:10:46.743 --> 01:10:48.743
- Just...
- (liquid pouring)

1260
01:10:48.970 --> 01:10:50.578
Pretend like you're
having fun.

1261
01:10:58.663 --> 01:10:59.754
To you.

1262
01:11:01.407 --> 01:11:05.242
- To me?
- Yeah.

1263
01:11:05.262 --> 01:11:06.744
(glasses clinking)

1264
01:11:06.763 --> 01:11:09.822
For showing me how naive I was

1265
01:11:09.841 --> 01:11:12.517
About how the world works.

1266
01:11:14.938 --> 01:11:17.830
- I showed you that?
- Yes, you did.

1267
01:11:17.849 --> 01:11:19.691
And so much more.

1268
01:11:22.687 --> 01:11:26.522
She is a ruthless liar and
master manipulator,

1269
01:11:26.674 --> 01:11:31.193
Out to ruin the life of every
man she meets.

1270
01:11:31.288 --> 01:11:33.955
My name is tess parks.

1271
01:11:34.106 --> 01:11:37.292
I've known ashley morris
a very long time.

1272
01:11:37.443 --> 01:11:39.368
(thudding at door)

1273
01:11:39.521 --> 01:11:41.537
...Ruthless liar and master
manipulator.

1274
01:11:41.689 --> 01:11:43.781
- (thudding)
- (grunting)

1275
01:11:43.875 --> 01:11:46.467
- (whimpering)
- tess?

1276
01:11:46.694 --> 01:11:48.619
- How did you find me?
- Ashley did.

1277
01:11:48.713 --> 01:11:50.530
With some help.

1278
01:11:50.548 --> 01:11:52.365
(groaning)

1279
01:11:52.458 --> 01:11:53.474
- You all right?
- Yeah.

1280
01:11:53.626 --> 01:11:54.700
Yeah, is she okay?

1281
01:11:54.794 --> 01:11:57.036
Yeah, she's fine. She's fine.

1282
01:11:57.055 --> 01:11:58.813
I'll tell you more on the way.
Come on!

1283
01:12:06.047 --> 01:12:08.823
(soft jazz playing)

1284
01:12:11.069 --> 01:12:12.827
You don't like your wine?

1285
01:12:15.665 --> 01:12:17.573
Trying to keep my mind clear.

1286
01:12:17.725 --> 01:12:19.559
